SyncState *

IMAPACcount uni
Host outlook.office365.com
User UNI_ADDR
PassCmd "gpg2 --decrypt --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -q ~/Mail/.config/uni.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
SystemCertificates yes

IMAPStore uni-remote
Account uni

MaildirStore uni-local
Path ~/Mail/Uni/
Inbox ~/Mail/Uni

